                    <h4 style="margin-top: 20px;">How to become a member?</h3>
                    <hr>

                    <p><strong>INDIVIDUAL MEMBERSHIP CATEGORIES</strong></p>
                    <p>The individual membership of the Association consists of:</p>
                    <ol>
                    <li>- Associate Member</li>
                    <li>- Member</li>
                    <li>- Fellow</li>
                    </ol>
                    <p style="margin-top: 50px;"><strong>INDIVIDUAL MEMBERSHIP REQUIREMENTS</strong></p>
                    <p><strong>Associate Member</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                    <li>- Treasury Staff between 1 to 5 years experience in Treasury related functions</li>
                    <li>- TDC/TMC/ACI or FMDA Exemption Certificate (Basic Level)</li>
                    <li>- Annual Membership Fee: N15,000</li>
                    <li>
                        <p><em>N.B: Any person that is an Associate Member is entitled (so long as he remains an Associate Member) to use with his/her name the designatory initials <strong>“AMFM”</strong> adopted.</em></p>  
                    </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Member</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                    <li>- Treasury Staff with above 5 years but less than 10 years experience in Treasury related functions</li>
                    <li>- TDC/TMC/ACI, TMC (Intermediate Level) or FMDA Exemption Certificate (Intermediate Level)</li>
                    <li>- Annual Membership Fee: N30,000.00</li>
                    <li>
                        <p><em>N.B: Any person that is a Member is (so long as he remains a member) entitled to use with his/her name, the designatory initials <strong>“MFM”.</strong></em></p>
                    </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Fellow</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                    <li>- Treasury Staff with at least 10 years experience in Treasury related functions</li>
                    <li>- TDC/ACI , TMC (Intermediate Level) or FMDA Exemption Certificate (Advance Level)</li>
                    <li>- Annual Membership Fee: N50,000.00</li>
                    <li>
                        <p><em>N.B: Any person that is a Fellow is (so long as he remains a member) entitled to use with his/her name, the designatory initials <strong>“FFM</strong></em></p>
                    </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>REGISTRATION REQUIREMENTS</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                    <li>- A copy of completed Individual Membership Registration Form</li>
                    <li>- One copy of:
                    <ul>
                    <li>- Comprehensive CV stating current and all previous job(s) history</li>
                    <li>- Treasury Certifications/Exemption Certificate and any other Professional Certifications</li>
                    <li>- 1 passport photo</li>
                    </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>Draft for Membership Fee</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>BENEFITS OF MEMBERSHIP</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                    <li>- Referencing from the Association</li>
                    <li>- Participation in the Association’s Committees</li>
                    <li>- Participating in the FMDA Workgroups and Council Elections</li>
                    <li>- Occupying Executive Position in the Association</li>
                    <li>- Access to Market Information</li>
                    <li>- Participation in market meetings</li>
                    <li>- Listed on the Authorised Dealers Directory</li>
                    <li>- Access to Members’ network Community etc.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p style="float: right;">
                        <a href="/register_individual" class="btn btn-primary">Proceed to registration</a>
                        <a href="/" class="btn btn-danger">Cancel</a>
                    </p>
                    
